metadata.name: Hish Hash Mish Mash #21
metadata.description:
To celebrate FxHash turning one this week...

25% of primary goes to Processing Foundation
25% of primary goes to Three.js
25% of primary goes to Hydra

The algorithm takes the hash and presents it to the viewer as a string, as binary code and as hex code.

Shapes are added to provide composition to each piece.
